## Getting Started

### Installation

```bash
# Install dependencies
poetry install

# Or with pip
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### Configuration

1. Copy `.env.example` to `.env`:
   ```bash
   cp .env.example .env
   ```

2. Update `.env` with your settings (especially `DATABASE_URL`)

### Running Migrations

```bash
# Run all migrations
fastappkit migrate all

# Or run individually
fastappkit migrate core upgrade
```

### Development Server

```bash
fastappkit core dev
```

Or with uvicorn directly:
```bash
uvicorn main:app --reload
```

