## Creating Apps

### Internal App

```bash
fastappkit app new blog
```

### External App (Package)

```bash
fastappkit app new blog --as-package
```

## Adding Apps

Edit `fastappkit.toml` and add apps to the `apps` list:

```toml
[tool.fastappkit]
apps = [
    "apps.blog",
    "apps.auth",
]
```
